on our honeymoon?

37
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:46,870
The Hotel Paraiso.

38
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:49,030
We sure were happy then

39
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:52,707
We still are.
This is just a bad streak.

40
00:03:52,940 --> 00:03:54,226
I'll tell you what

41
00:03:54,540 --> 00:03:58,261
You're going to put on this shirt
you look so great in,

42
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,980
which I gave you with all my love,

43
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:02,790
and you're going to cheer up.

44
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:04,710
I can't.

45
00:04:04,940 --> 00:04:07,102
Why are you so depressed today?

46
