I've ever done.

50
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:23,591
"Coca-Cola. Life's little spark."

51
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:26,023
That wasn't bad.

52
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:27,062
Wasn't bad?

53
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:29,462
They still use it on commercials.

54
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,350
- That was ages ago.
- Look.

55
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:33,548
I know you're having a hard time,

56
00:04:33,860 --> 00:04:36,067
