57
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:38,189
than we are.
You'll get that job

58
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:41,185
and we'll take a trip
with the money.

59
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:42,910
Our anniversary is the 14th

60
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:44,426
That's right.

61
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:46,141
Our anniversary.

62
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:49,069
But I still have two weeks.

63
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:51,268
We can go to that hotel.

64
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:54,103
We'll stay in the same room.

65
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:55,546
