Come here.

72
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,988
I gotta go, I gotta go...

73
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:20,063
I don't want to be late.

74
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:25,064
- I'd like to teach the world to sing...
- Silly.

75
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:28,221
In perfect harmony...

76
00:05:28,540 --> 00:05:31,703
Luisa, please, I have to go,

77
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:34,142
or late is what I'll be...

78
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:36,109
Good luck. Got everything?

79
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:38,149
Wallet, phone, keys?

80
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:40,827
I think so

81
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:44,706
Want me to come with you?

82
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:46,465
