83
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:56,428
- Good morning.
- One moment.

84
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:59,106
Mckenzie Emerson Spain
may I help you?

85
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,262
I'll connect you

86
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,467
Good morning.

87
