89
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:09,025
- Name?
- Javier Gandara.

90
00:07:09,260 --> 00:07:09,829
No, yours.

91
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:11,471
Roberto Gomez.

92
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:14,667
Roberto Gomez is here.
He says he's early.

93
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:16,743
What should I do with him?

94
