Take my hand!

246
00:17:46,860 --> 00:17:48,703
Here! Hey! No!

247
00:17:48,940 --> 00:17:50,749
- I can't!
- God!

248
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:52,990
Please, help me!

249
00:17:53,220 --> 00:17:54,381
Give me your hand

250
00:17:54,620 --> 00:17:55,667
Help!

251
00:17:56,940 --> 00:17:58,385
We got you!

252
00:17:58,620 --> 00:18:00,463
- Jump!
- Don't let go!

253
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:02,828
Jump, for God's sake!

254
00:18:04,860 --> 00:18:07,022
I'll get help!
Hold on!

255
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:08,381
Help!

256
00:18:11,140 --> 00:18:12,505
Help!

257
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:17,591
Help!

258
00:18:20,780 --> 00:18:22,748
Help me, please!

259
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:25,705
Help!

260
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:28,948
I'm slipping, I can't hold on!

261
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:39,586
Good lord!

262
00:18:40,100 --> 00:18:41,625
- No!
- Where is he?

263
00:18:42,660 --> 00:18:46,221
Get help and call an ambulance.
Quickly!

264
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:47,950
Enough introductions.

265
00:18:48,180 --> 00:18:51,263
Let us enjoy the efforts
of the last few years.

