Can you get UP?

277
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:17,147
Is it your back?

278
00:19:17,380 --> 00:19:19,348
No, I can't move my head.

279
00:19:19,580 --> 00:19:20,627
I can't.

280
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:24,826
What's wrong?

281
00:19:25,380 --> 00:19:26,825
Nothing, don't worry.

282
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:28,943
[- What are you guys doing?
- What's up]

283
00:19:29,180 --> 00:19:31,069
- He needs an ambulance.
- It's on the way.

284
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:32,142
Now, damn it!

285
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:36,829
We had a hard time finding it,
because at first we thought

286
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:38,744
- one of the neighbors...
- Excuse me.

287
00:19:38,980 --> 00:19:40,903
Can we go outside already?

288
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:43,825
I need to send the article
to the paper before it closes.

289
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:45,665
Why can't I move my head?

290
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:47,260
Stay still.

291
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:49,269
- It's okay.
- What's going on?

292
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:51,980
You see those rods over there?

293
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:55,185
You have one stuck in your head.

294
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:56,467
What?

295
00:19:58,060 --> 00:20:00,028
It's okay, the ambulance
is on the way.

296
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:02,262
I need to call my wife.

297
00:20:05,660 --> 00:20:07,469
Hey! Where are you going?

298
00:20:07,780 --> 00:20:10,431
- What's going on here?
- Please! Listen for a second.

299
00:20:10,660 --> 00:20:14,665
It took centuries to discover
this ancient marvel.

300
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:18,385
I want to be the one
who turns on the lights.

301
00:20:18,660 --> 00:20:20,469
Is that too much to ask?

302
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:22,509
What hospital will they take me to?

303
00:20:22,740 --> 00:20:24,981
Perpetuo Socorro.
It's five minutes away.

304
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:26,665
Perpetuo Socorro.

305
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:28,664
Relax.

306
00:20:35,140 --> 00:20:38,701
Hi, honey. Why haven't you called?
How was the meeting?

307
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:40,943
Fine. Listen...

308
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:44,468
Something absurd happened,
you'll laugh.

309
00:20:44,700 --> 00:20:47,544
I had a little accident and I have
an iron rod stuck in my head.

310
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:48,747
You have what?

311
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:50,505
I had a little accident.

312
00:20:50,740 --> 00:20:53,664
Hello? Roberto?
I can't hear you.

313
00:20:53,900 --> 00:20:57,063
I said I have an iron rod
stuck in my head.

314
00:20:57,300 --> 00:20:59,462
You slipped on an iron bed?

315
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:00,587
You don't understand!

316
00:21:00,820 --> 00:21:02,424
Hello? Roberto?

317
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:05,587
Roberto?
Listen, are you okay?

318
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:07,743
I'm fine.
I'm waiting for the ambulance.

319
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:08,902
The ambulance?

320
00:21:09,140 --> 00:21:12,303
They're taking me to Perpetuo Socorro.
I'm in Cartage.

321
00:21:12,540 --> 00:21:15,544
Okay.
Socorro, Cartage, ambulance.

322
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:19,982
I'm leaving right now. Why Carta...?
Never mind, I'm on my way.

323
00:21:25,780 --> 00:21:27,305
Are you calmer now?

324
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,427
Yeah.

325
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:30,260
I'm better.

326
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:32,105
Is there a lot of blood?

327
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:35,223
I don't see any blood.

328
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:37,743
Careful, damn it!

329
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:39,823
- Where's the ambulance?
- It's almost here.

330
00:21:40,300 --> 00:21:41,711
Take it easy, okay?

331
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:43,544
The ambulance is almost here.

332
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:45,782
What's he doing with his cell phone?

333
00:21:46,020 --> 00:21:47,260
Stop that!

334
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:51,351
- Better?
- Yeah, better.

335
00:21:51,580 --> 00:21:52,945
Feeling any calmer?

336
00:21:53,700 --> 00:21:55,782
By the way, my name is Roberto.

337
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:57,262
Claudio.

338
00:21:58,020 --> 00:21:58,907
Sorry.

339
00:21:59,540 --> 00:22:01,668
Sorry we met like this, Roberto.

340
00:22:02,060 --> 00:22:03,107
Damn.

341
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:06,271
I was only looking
for the Hotel Paraiso.

342
00:22:06,540 --> 00:22:09,271
They closed it a couple years ago
to build the theater museum.

343
00:22:09,540 --> 00:22:12,111
Theater? What theater?

344
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:23,029
It's grandiose, Merche.

345
00:22:24,460 --> 00:22:26,030
Grandiose.

346
00:22:27,980 --> 00:22:29,744
There's a man down there!

347
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:31,186
- What?
- You're rig ht.

348
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:32,626
It looks like an accident.

349
