when they hear his story?

1065
00:55:41,060 --> 00:55:45,224
"I went to see my friends at McKenzie
and decided to kill myself."

1066
00:55:45,660 --> 00:55:48,391
They can't blame us
for him trying to kill himself.

1067
00:55:48,620 --> 00:55:51,908
If we can't control our own media image,
what will our clients think?

1068
00:55:52,140 --> 00:55:54,871
- Hire him right now.
- We have no openings.

1069
00:55:55,940 --> 00:55:56,941
Yes, we do.

1070
00:55:57,620 --> 00:55:58,667
His.

1071
00:55:59,420 --> 00:56:01,263
Okay. I'm on my way.

1072
00:56:01,780 --> 00:56:02,667
Sorry.

1073
00:56:03,060 --> 00:56:04,391
If you wanted the deal,

1074
00:56:04,620 --> 00:56:07,749
you should have taken my call
and talked to me.

1075
00:56:07,980 --> 00:56:08,947
Look, kid.

1076
00:56:09,180 --> 00:56:10,750
You said you accepted our offer.

1077
00:56:10,980 --> 00:56:14,268
