to my client.

1078
00:56:14,500 --> 00:56:17,868
Give me 300 thousand
or I'll play the market.

1079
00:56:18,100 --> 00:56:19,625
I told you it's not worth that.

1080
00:56:19,860 --> 00:56:20,782
It isn't?

1081
00:56:22,140 --> 00:56:23,551
What if he dies?

1082
00:56:23,820 --> 00:56:25,060
What do you mean?

1083
00:56:25,300 --> 00:56:26,267
Think about it

1084
00:56:27,220 --> 00:56:30,542
Why doesn't anybody remember
the Chilean miners?

1085
00:56:31,580 --> 00:56:33,423
Because they lived.

1086
00:56:33,660 --> 00:56:35,424
If this guy dies,

1087
00:56:35,660 --> 00:56:37,150
