1091
00:56:42,580 --> 00:56:43,627
A legend.

1092
00:56:43,860 --> 00:56:46,670
His last words will be
the New Testament.

1093
00:56:46,900 --> 00:56:47,947
You thin k so?

1094
00:56:48,260 --> 00:56:51,787
Tomorrow every channel in the world
will kill for that interview.

1095
00:56:52,860 --> 00:56:53,941
All right.

1096
00:56:54,780 --> 00:56:56,908
