Hey, we have money now.

1565
01:21:46,580 --> 01:21:48,264
You can study anything you want.

1566
01:21:48,580 --> 01:21:50,423
You getting well
is all that matters.

1567
01:21:50,740 --> 01:21:52,708
I'm serious, son.

1568
01:21:53,140 --> 01:21:54,949
Do anything you want, okay?

1569
01:21:55,700 --> 01:21:57,748
What you think is what matters.

1570
01:21:57,980 --> 01:21:59,744
Not what other people think

